            {
              "originalPosition": 274,
              "body": "This subsection is ambiguous. We indicate that a non tls peer can fallback to tcp-ao and then BGP operates never over plaintext TCP.",
              "createdAt": "2026-07-02T12:59:15Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-07-02T13:15:40Z"
            },
            {
              "originalPosition": 247,
              "body": "We probably need to define active and passive peer because this is different from current BGP. An active peer sends immediately a ClientHello. A passive peer waits for a ClientHello.",
              "createdAt": "2026-07-02T13:02:31Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-07-02T13:15:40Z"
            },
            {
              "originalPosition": 331,
              "body": "I would use session instead of tunnel.",
              "createdAt": "2026-07-02T13:04:11Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-07-02T13:15:40Z"
            },
            {
              "originalPosition": 335,
              "body": "Should we write an active BGP peer?",
              "createdAt": "2026-07-02T13:04:43Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-07-02T13:15:40Z"
            },
            {
              "originalPosition": 347,
              "body": "Should we write passive BGP peer ?",
              "createdAt": "2026-07-02T13:05:10Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-07-02T13:15:40Z"
            },
            {
              "originalPosition": 376,
              "body": "We should use the words active and passive in this section.",
              "createdAt": "2026-07-02T13:05:58Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-07-02T13:15:40Z"
            },
            {
              "originalPosition": 396,
              "body": "It could be possible to add the BGP identifier in the ALPN, like botls-1.2.3.4 with the router id, but this would create a lot of complexity\n",
              "createdAt": "2026-07-02T13:09:07Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-07-02T13:15:40Z"
            },
            {
              "originalPosition": 427,
              "body": "validation only during establishment ?",
              "createdAt": "2026-07-02T13:10:00Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-07-02T13:15:40Z"
            },
            {
              "originalPosition": 437,
              "body": "I would start with this paragraph\n",
              "createdAt": "2026-07-02T13:10:40Z",
              "updatedAt": "2026-07-02T13:15:40Z"
